{
  "texts": [
    "• SocKET (Choi et al, 2023).",
    "The SocKET dataset encompasses around 2.6M English test samples drawn from 58 NLP datasets designed to assess social knowledge.",
    "It functions as a benchmark for evaluating LLMs' proficiency in comprehending various aspects of social knowledge, categorized into humor and sarcasm, aggression, emotion, credibility, and social facts.",
    "The task types encompass classification, regression, pair-wise comparison, and span identification.",
    "• InfiniteBench (Zhang et al, 2023j)."
  ]
}